0.3.0
-----
* Extended testsuites
* Project moved to openSUSE/rubygem-zypper at GitHub
* Using Nori (with Nokogiri) to parse the XML output
* Speedup improvements
* New Package::updates method

0.2.2
-----
* Fixed last_exit_status method and thus all methods returning boolean

0.2.1
-----
* Debugging output turned off

0.2.0
-----
* Split into smaller one-task libraries
* Added plural aliases for for accessing subclasses (patch -> patches,
  package -> packages, ...)
* Generic package search
* Extended Patch with applicable?() and install() methods
* Added testsuites
* Packaging into gem

0.1.0
-----
* Initial implementation using POpen4
* Added Services and Repositories handling
* Added Packages and Packages handling
* Added documentation
